snippet.title: Black Rose Expansion (Story Mode) Teaser *RELEASED*
snippet.description:
The expansion is now live at Game Jolt: http://gamejolt.com/games/other/black-rose/59833/  *THIS IS NOT MINECRAFT, YOUTUBE*

Here's a quick (and sloppy) teaser for the Black Rose "Story Mode" expansion! :D Credit for the intro music (music box 1D56) goes to Setuniman from freesound.org.
